'''镶嵌地块''' (Tessera)是[[金星|金星]]表面地形严重变形的区域，其特征是由两个或两个以上高地势、高雷达反向散射的交错[[地质构造|构造]]单元所构成<ref name=Bind>{{cite journal |last1=Bindschadler |first1=Duane |last2=Head |first2=James |title=Tessera Terrain, Venus: Characterization and Models for Origin and Evolution |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research |date=1991 |volume=96 |issue=B4 |pages=5889–5907 |doi=10.1029/90jb02742 |bibcode=1991JGR....96.5889B}}</ref>。镶嵌地块通常代表金星表面所有确定位置上最古老的地层和构造最变形的地形<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ivers |first1=Carol |last2=McGill |first2=George |title=Kinematics of a Tessera Block in the Vellamo Planitia Quadrangle |journal=Lunar and Planetary Science |volume=29 }}</ref><ref name="Hansen Ribbon Terrain">{{cite journal |last1=Hansen |first1=Vicki |last2=Willis |first2=James |title=Ribbon Terrain Formation, Southwestern Fortuna Tessera, Venus: Implications for Lithosphere Evolution |journal=Icarus |date=1998 |volume=132 |issue=2 |pages=321–343 |doi=10.1006/icar.1998.5897 |bibcode=1998Icar..132..321H|url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/ceccbb3d587e158566c0adc56887b76dcc15131f }}</ref>。镶嵌地块存在多种类型，目前尚不清楚这是否由金星[[地幔|地幔]]与局部[[地壳|地壳]]或[[岩石圈|岩石圈]]应力相互作用的不同而导致，抑或这些不同的地形代表了高原地壳在形成和下沉时间轴上的不同位置<ref name="Hansen Issues" />。目前有多种解释镶嵌地块形成的理论模型，要完全了解这种复杂的地形，有必要对金星表面作进一步深入的研究。

==探索==
[[先驱者金星计划|先驱者金星轨道飞行器]]探测到异常的雷达特性和高反向散射区域，金星15号和金星16号轨道飞行器通过[[合成孔径雷达|合成孔径雷达]](SAR)成像，揭示了这些区域呈现杂乱的“瓷砖”地形，[[前苏联|前苏联]]科学家将其命名为“Паркет”(镶木地板)，后来被称为“镶嵌地块”(Tesserae)<ref>Barsukov, V.L., et al, "The geology of Venus according to the results of an analysis of radar images obtained by Venera-15 and Venera-16 Preliminary data", Geokhimiya, Dec. 1984</ref><ref name=Head>{{cite journal |last1=Head |first1=James |title=Venus Trough and Ridge Tessera: Anolog to Earth Oceanic Crust Formed at Spreading Centers? |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research |date=1990 |volume=95 |issue=B5 |pages=7119–7132 |doi=10.1029/jb095ib05p07119 |bibcode=1990JGR....95.7119H}}</ref>。有关镶嵌地形的最新数据来自[[麦哲伦号金星探测器|麦哲伦号金星探测器]]，该探测器高分辨率(约100米/像素)测绘了金星大部分表面 <ref name="Hansen short" />，未来的金星探索计划将有助于进一步了解镶嵌地形。

==位置==
目前已辨识出镶嵌地形占金星地表7.3%的区域，总计面积约33.2×10<sup>6</sup>公里<sup>2</sup>，主要分布在少数几处较大的区域内<ref name=Ivanov>{{cite journal |last1=Ivanov |first1=Mikhail |last2=Head |first2=James |title=Global Geologic Map of Venus |journal=Planetary and Space Science |date=2011 |volume=59 |issue=13 |pages=1559–1600 |doi=10.1016/j.pss.2011.07.008 |bibcode=2011P&SS...59.1559I}}</ref>，高度集中于东经0°到东经150°之间，代表了从[[阿佛洛狄忒高地|阿佛洛狄忒高地]]地壳延展中心到[[伊师塔地|伊什塔尔高地]]地壳会聚中心间这一大片区域内<ref name=Bind />。镶嵌地块几乎完全暴露在金星的[[高原|高原]]地壳内。镶嵌地块的内露层，即高原地壳中未发现镶嵌地形的区域，被认为是高原地壳的崩塌区<ref name="Hansen short">{{cite journal |last1=Hansen |first1=Vicki |last2=Banks |first2=Brian |last3=Ghent |first3=Rebecca |title=Tessera terrain and crustal plateaus, Venus |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_geology_1999-12_27_12/page/1071 |journal=Geology |date=1999 |volume=27 |issue=12 |pages=1071–1074 |doi=10.1130/0091-7613(1999)027<1071:ttacpv>2.3.co;2|bibcode=1999Geo....27.1071H }}</ref><ref name=Romeo /><ref name=Campbell>{{cite journal |last1=Campbell |first1=Bruce |last2=Campbell |first2=Donald |last3=Morgan |first3=Gareth |last4=Carter |first4=Lynn |last5=Nolan |first5=Micael |title=Evidence for crater ejecta on Venus tessera terrain from Earth-based radar images |journal=Icarus |date=2015 |volume=250 |pages=123–130 |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2014.11.025 |bibcode=2015Icar..250..123C|url=https://repository.si.edu/bitstream/handle/10088/25019/nasm_201467CE.pdf }}</ref>。大面积的镶嵌地块以它们所处的纬度进行标记，赤道和南纬地区的被标记为“区”(Regio)，而北纬地区的则被标记为“镶嵌地块”(Tesserae) <ref name=Venus2>{{cite book |last1=Bougher |first1=Steven |last2=Hunten |first2=Donald |last3=Phillips |first3=Roger |title=Venus II : Geology, Geophysics, Atmosphere, and Solar Wind Environment |date=1997 |publisher=[[University_of_Arizona_Press|University of Arizona Press]] |isbn=978-0816518302 }}</ref>。

